race.comment: DARYTE (1) didn't jump favourite on debut but put her rivals to the sword, landing midfield and running away to win impressively over 1000m. The rise in trip only looks to favour her more and Pike remains in the saddle from an inside draw. Up in weight now, but she looks above average and can repeat the dose. FARNOVA (7) jumped fav ahead of DARYTE on debut and led the field up, but was no match for the winner. Can roll forward once again from the draw and she'll be better for the debut effort. Wouldn't surprise to turn the table. PROPERATA (2) was solid on debut 56 days ago and has been back to the trials since where he was impressive. Drawn wide here which is the query, but he brings in a different formline and is worth thought. HERE THE BOOM (11) has shown good speed at the trials coming in and is not to be discounted. PERFUME PRINCESS (8) comes through the DARYTE race and looks better suited out in trip slightly.
